<paragraph id="AB0E403F27420F78FC8FF8D740AA8182" blockId="2.[831,1437,1513,2049]" pageId="2" pageNumber="259">Pads of lamella postvaginalis narrow, bristled; Ostium and nearly the entire ductus bursae funnel-shaped, more strongly sclerotized, in corpus bursae numerous rows of small, stronger sclerotized thorns.</paragraph>
